{"tid":178923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【shit! shit!】東涌泳池有便便 康文署封池消毒 明早重開","createTime":"2017-03-30T01:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T06:19:52.000Z","uid":73262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25970c34e17a9ff7e36b388dda0354ba64a3756f","tid":178923,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:19:41.000Z","msg":"康樂及文化事務署宣布，由於在離島區東涌游泳池發現有少量糞便，該游泳池現已暫時關閉，以便進行清潔消毒。游泳池預計於明日上午6時30分重開。<br />\n<br />\n康文署呼籲泳客顧己及人，合力保持泳池清潔衞生，落水前不要吃得過飽，有需要應先使用洗手間。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56497603&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56497603%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170329&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f14d355c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56497603%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170329&h=2dc518d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56497603&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170329</a>"},{"pid":"5a5261c1f91c14d7c675e160382a7220b891537b","tid":178923,"uid":39853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"冇事嘅，當飲左啖朱古力囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c949f1c5785ceb9d462a23ad6db96061e6ccd692","tid":178923,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"同睇電影一樣，有屎屎尿尿先開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68845d0da2a5aa97d1117e14a6a9ffa96a5ebf1","tid":178923,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"有糞可以睇見，有屎又點樣check?"},{"pid":"39ab6acd582ca34a2493562090d2cf05e16bd1e4","tid":178923,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"